 faster than expected.</p><p>I ve been refining my own vibe stack lately.<br>Building with @Google Antigravity at the core. It keeps the flow clean when things get messy.</p><p>Share your current Vibe Stack:</p>", "featuredAt": null, "pinned": false, "user": {"id": "7478224", "name": "Kashyap Rathod", "username": "kashyaprathod", "avatarUrl": "https://ph-avatars.imgix.net/7478224/adb107e4-f74c-44d8-aaee-ff831d767be2.jpeg", "__typename": "User", "isAccountVerified": false, "isAmbassador": false, "selectedBylineProduct": null, "topProductBadge": null, "topHunterBadge": null, "topLaunchBadge": null}, "hasVoted": false, "votesCount": 23, "__typename": "DiscussionThread", "commentsCount": 13, "featuredComment": null, "primaryForum": {"id": "472520", "slug": "vibecoding", "subject": {"id": "201", "name": "Vibecoding", "thumbnailUuid": "379b8fc1-a8e0-48f3-be0c-15e11b165944.svg", "__typename": "DiscussionCategory"}, "__typename": "DiscussionForumType"}}, "__typename": "DiscussionThreadEdge"}, {"node": {"id": "804492", "pageViewsCount": 173, "slug": "post-launch-thoughts-after-reaching-top-10-on-product-hunt", "createdAt": "2026-01-13T00:00:00-08:00", "path": "/p/intrascope-app/post-launch-thoughts-after-reaching-top-10-on-product-hunt", "title": "Post-launch thoughts after reaching Top 10 on Product Hunt", "descriptionPreview": "<p>Hey everyone,</p><p>After launching Intrascope and finishing Top 10 Product of the Day, we wanted to open a quick discussion.</p><p>The biggest takeaway for us wasn t the ranking, but the conversations. We talked to teams who are already using AI daily and are struggling with scattered tools, separate API keys, lost context, and costs growing without visibility.</p><p>That s exactly why we built Intrascope: a shared AI workspace where teams bring their own API keys, work with shared context and Manifests, and keep usage and costs predictable.</p>", "featuredAt": "2026-01-13", "pinned": false, "user": {"id": "9243405", "name": "Vladimir", "usernam